AMENDMENTS TO LB203
Introduced by Fredrickson, 20.
1 1. On page 8, line 23, strike "the next regularly scheduled meeting
2 of the board" and insert "a regular or emergency meeting of the board.
3 Any duties required to be carried out by a public body under this
4 subdivision may be completed using virtual conferencing when permitted
5 under subsection (7) of section 84-1411. For purposes of this
6 subdivision, written includes electronic records or documents".
7 2. On page 9, line 26, strike "the next regularly scheduled meeting
8 of the board" and insert "a regular or emergency meeting of the board.
9 Any duties required to be carried out by a public body under this
10 subdivision may be completed using virtual conferencing when permitted
11 under subsection (7) of section 84-1411. For purposes of this
12 subdivision, written or in writing includes electronic records or
13 documents".
